channel.title: [RS2] Srl - Fletcher/Stringer and Cow Killer
channel.description:
[SIZE=2][FONT=Franklin Gothic Medium]
[size=20pt][center]Both Scripts Need Srl ! get it at [url=http://www.villavu.com/forums/]http://www.villavu.com/forums/[/url] [/center]
[CENTER]- Srl Cow Fighter Version 1.00 -[/CENTER]
[CENTER]--------------------------------------------------------[/CENTER]
Version: 1.1
Description: Fights cows at lumbride, trains to specific level or amount of time. Uses the player array and when you die it will go back for more.
Known Bugs: Sometimes gets lost and goes to goblins.
Notes: Must have SRL !, also you will need to save "CowPic" in the same place as the script.
Setup: Make sure first account starts between the exits of Lumbridge, all other account start at cow field.
[CENTER]Form: [URL=http://"http://imageshack.us"][IMG]http://img306.imageshack.us/img306/7900/form7bh.png[/img][/URL] [/CENTER]
[CENTER]--------------------------------------------------------[/CENTER]
[SIZE=2][FONT=Franklin Gothic Medium] [CENTER]- Srl Fletcher -[/CENTER]
Version: 1
Description: Fletches Logs, Strings Unstrungs or Makes Arrows.
Notes: Post all bugs here !
Setup: Stand next to a bank with neccesary equipment.
[CENTER]--------------------------------------------------------[/CENTER]
If you have any questions please contact me on [EMAIL="Spky.S@hotmail.com"]Spky.S@hotmail.com[/EMAIL]
Thanks, Spky
